    <TwoColumnContentBlock
    
    title="SEO and Digital Marketing"
    image={seo2}
    imageAlt="SEO"
    titleColor="black"
    href="/"
    linkText="Get Started Today"
  >
    <Fragment slot="content" >
      <p class="my-4">
        It can be difficult to know where to start when it comes to Search Engine Optimisation. You might feel overwhelmed and unsure of what exactly to do or where to turn.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Let us take care of everything for you. We will produce a range of lightning-fast, highly-optimized landing pages to boost your online presence and give you the edge over the competition.</p>
      <p class="mb-4">
        More pages means that your site ranks higher on search results when people look for your products or services. This means more people finding your website, more orders, and more growth for your business. 
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4">
        We also offer a comprehensive local SEO service to provide your business with all the essential tools and strategies it requires for success in your local area.
      </p>
      <p>Get in touch today to begin your journey to digital success.</p>
    </Fragment>
  </TwoColumnContentBlock>



  <div class="bg-gray-900 py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
        <h2 class="text-base lg:text-xl font-semibold leading-7 text-easynet-orange">How it Works
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl">Targeted landing pages for increased website traffic</p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">By having more pages on your website you're seen as more authoritative by search engines. You also increase your chances of being found.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-none">
        <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2">
          
            <div class="flex flex-col">
            <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-2xl leading-7 text-white">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#ff9a02" class="w-16 h-16">
