             <span class="font-bold">Enhanced Visibility</span>
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
              <p class="flex-auto">Landing pages can be tailored to specific keywords and topics related to your business. When people search for these keywords, your optimized landing pages are more likely to appear in search engine results, increasing your website's visibility.</p>
              
            </dd>
          </div>
          

          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-2xl leading-7 text-white">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#ff9a02" class="w-16 h-16">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3.22 3.22a.75.75 0 011.06 0l3.97 3.97V4.5a.75.75 0 011.5 0V9a.75.75 0 01-.75.75H4.5a.75.75 0 010-1.5h2.69L3.22 4.28a.75.75 0 010-1.06zm17.56 0a.75.75 0 010 1.06l-3.97 3.97h2.69a.75.75 0 010 1.5H15a.75.75 0 01-.75-.75V4.5a.75.75 0 011.5 0v2.69l3.97-3.97a.75.75 0 011.06 0zM3.75 15a.75.75 0 01.75-.75H9a.75.75 0 01.75.75v4.5a.75.75 0 01-1.5 0v-2.69l-3.97 3.97a.75.75 0 01-1.06-1.06l3.97-3.97H4.5a.75.75 0 01-.75-.75zm10.5 0a.75.75 0 01.75-.75h4.5a.75.75 0 010 1.5h-2.69l3.97 3.97a.75.75 0 11-1.06 1.06l-3.97-3.97v2.69a.75.75 0 01-1.5 0V15z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  
                  
                  
                  
             <span class="font-bold">Targeted Audience</span>
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
              <p class="flex-auto">
                Landing pages allow you to address different segments of your audience. By creating content that caters to their specific interests or needs, you're more likely to attract and retain visitors who are genuinely interested in your products or services.
             </p>
             
            </dd>
          </div>
          

          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-2xl leading-7 text-white">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#ff9a02" class="w-16 h-16">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.47 2.47a.75.75 0 011.06 0l7.5 7.5a.75.75 0 11-1.06 1.06l-6.22-6.22V21a.75.75 0 01-1.5 0V4.81l-6.22 6.22a.75.75 0 11-1.06-1.06l7.5-7.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
